Quest:Always Have MooShu

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Et Tu, Lili?

Given By: Lili Ma

Giver Location: Tatakai Outpost
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Defeat Ashikata in his lair
Talk to Lili Ma
Hand In: Lili Ma

Reward:

176
2,085
Incense Plate
Spectral Blast
Skeletal Pirate
Phoenix
Blight Hound
Earth Walker
Minotaur
Stormzilla

Leads to:

None

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Always Have MooShu should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Always Have MooShu in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
